title: Town of Night ALIAS
description:
Town of Night-ALiAS 

RELEASE
NOTES

Town of Night is a First-Person Dungeon Crawler inspired by games
like Shining in the Darkness, Etrian Odyssey, Diablo and Wizardry
In Town of Night you play as Corr Algrimm. Hero, Scholar, ladies'
man and expert Sword fighter - All self proclaimed

Corr is visiting the Town of Night, a strange little town that
makes money with Dungeon and Monster hunting tourism, to find out
where the monsters are coming from

In Town of Night you can recruit different members to your party to
go dungeon crawling like you want to
Remember to bring Ink and Paper to draw your own map and try not to
die

1. Unzip & Unrar
2. Run Setup.exe for install
3. Have Fun!!!
